long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
CXP SEED extension was developed to assist the San Francisco QA department with testing CXP content in CNOWV8 platform.  By clicking on the seed icon user is provided with SEED, NAME, URI, and TAKEiD of the question that they are currently on.
